Sentencas: Since 1958 Westinghouse has carried out research activities to develop solid oxide technology.
Titulo: SOLID OXIDE FUEL-CELL DEVELOPMENTS AT WESTINGHOUSE

Sentencas: Past activities have been well published and presented.

Sentencas: This paper will present recent activities carried out at Westinghouse concentrating on the last several years.

Sentencas: During this period, individual cell performance has exceeded 20 000 h of operation, while bundle and small generator performance has exceeded 5000 h of operation.
Titulo: SOLID OXIDE FUEL-CELL DEVELOPMENTS AT WESTINGHOUSE

Sentencas: Cells, bundles and generators up to 20 kW have been operated using pipeline natural gas.
Titulo: SOLID OXIDE FUEL-CELL DEVELOPMENTS AT WESTINGHOUSE

Sentencas: Cells of 50 cm length are now routinely made in small production campaigns while 77 cm long cells have been made in the laboratory.
Titulo: SOLID OXIDE FUEL-CELL DEVELOPMENTS AT WESTINGHOUSE

Sentencas: Production of 100 cm cells will be initiated this year.

Sentencas: Two 25 kW generators are currently in production for delivery late this year and early next year.
